short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Autonomously connect and engage with prospects

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
RightBound connector automatically finds and connects prospects on behalf of SDRs. RightBound connector reaches out to contacts who are less available or responsive via email and other communication channels. 

Once engaged, RightBound will push the lead directly into your sales development platform or CRM.

RightBound connector helps SDRs to boost their performance by increasing their volume of high-quality leads.
